{"tid":886679,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"異見漫畫家巴丟草香港作品展突取消　主辦單位稱收中國當局威脅","createTime":"2018-11-02T09:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T15:09:00.000Z","uid":48083,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d125b9dc5cf168c97bb3e44bd279ba4b4c4253e2","tid":886679,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:33:38.000Z","msg":"以定居澳洲的中國藝術家巴丟草作品為主題的展覽「共歌」，原訂今個星期六在香港黃竹坑一展覽場地開幕，香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒、訪港的俄羅斯抗爭者Pussy Riot都會應邀出席。但主辦單位今日發出聲明，宣布因為「安全考慮」展覽取消，更稱收到「中國當局有關巴丟草的威脅（threats made by the Chinese authorities）」。<br />\n<br />\n巴丟草作品展「共歌」，是由 Hong Kong Free Press、無國界記者和國際特赦組織主辦，原訂星期六晚開幕，主辦單位本來已表示，由於安全考慮，巴丟草不會來香港，而是會以數碼方式和現場人士互動。<br />\n<br />\n但 Hong Kong Free Press 今日下午就發聲明，指展覽要取消，聲明強調主辦單位重視言論自由，但同樣重視伙伴的安全，期望日後香港市民仍有機會可以看到巴丟草的作品。<br />\n<br />\n其中一個受邀出席開幕禮的嘉賓、香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒回覆立場時表示，基於安全考慮，尊重主辦單位的決定。 他認為，一個藝術家因為辦展覽而受威脅是暴行，譴責中國當局打壓香港爭取民主自由的人。希望終有一日會有機會在香港見到巴丟草的作品。<br />\n<br />\n巴丟草出生於中國上海，2011 年出國後，開始創作政治漫畫。作品題材批判中國社政問題，尤其關注諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波，多個創作以劉曉波夫婦為題。他亦有關心香港議題，曾繪畫黃之鋒、雨傘運動、旺角騷亂（魚蛋革命）、銅鑼灣書店事件等。畫作風格鮮明，其紅黑色調容易辨認。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》正向主辦單位及巴丟草了解詳情。<br />\n<br />\n部分巴丟草作品：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oSfwiM5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoSfwiM5.png&h=995ec4cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HDFoUku.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHDFoUku.png&h=5e3e1353&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iELwiM9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiELwiM9.png&h=d0d7d0aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tD2iJdQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtD2iJdQ.png&h=64c4cf1a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/46gSNFw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F46gSNFw.png&h=0b3dae2e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P9Fz00x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP9Fz00x.png&h=75604034&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PdZw3dT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPdZw3dT.png&h=93102621&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RJWrR7e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRJWrR7e.png&h=e883497b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他作品：<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/異見漫畫家巴丟草香港作品展突取消-主辦單位稱收中國當局威脅/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%95%B0%E8%A6%8B%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB%E5%AE%B6%E5%B7%B4%E4%B8%9F%E8%8D%89%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81%E5%B1%95%E7%AA%81%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88-%E4%B8%BB%E8%BE%A6%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E7%A8%B1%E6%94%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%2F&d=QEVk%2FwPgkJ%2FS4306LLtS%2FR4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=0cab00a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%95%B0%E8%A6%8B%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB%E5%AE%B6%E5%B7%B4%E4%B8%9F%E8%8D%89%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81%E5%B1%95%E7%AA%81%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88-%E4%B8%BB%E8%BE%A6%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E7%A8%B1%E6%94%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%2F&h=55310111\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/異見漫畫家巴丟草香港作品展突取消-主辦單位稱收中國當局威脅/</a>"},{"pid":"3651b3b2d8e2bc77694ee4cf002a1f1157a2c838","tid":886679,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:39:31.000Z","msg":"著草"},{"pid":"d5f0585173cb86ee8a1d7d4bfd5aa1d1f8c45f7d","tid":886679,"uid":113000,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:40:42.000Z","msg":"日本傳媒可以親身黎體驗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0681fdac8a8af8e333b05cd3334f51a894fabe8","tid":886679,"uid":90520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:42:01.000Z","msg":"佢咁做令我更想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos